author: admin
title: NVIDIA Sets Conference Call for Third-Quarter Financial Results
text:
Submitted by admin on 10/22/2015 @ 2:00 PM Companies mentioned in this article: NVIDIA 
SANTA CLARA, CA -- (Marketwired) -- 10/22/15 -- NVIDIA (NASDAQ: NVDA) will host a conference call on Thursday, Nov. 5, at 2 p.m. PT (5 p.m. ET) to discuss its financial results for the third quarter of fiscal year 2016, ending Oct. 25, 2015. 
The call will be webcast live (in listen-only mode) at the following websites: www.nvidia.com and www.streetevents.com . The company's prepared remarks will be followed by a question and answer session, which will be limited to questions from financial analysts and institutional investors. 
Ahead of the call, NVIDIA will provide written commentary on its third-quarter results from its CFO. This material will be posted to www.nvidia.com/ir immediately after the company's results are publicly announced at approximately 1:20 p.m. PT. 
To listen to the conference call, dial (303) 223-2699; no password is required. 
A replay of the conference call will be available until Nov. 12, 2015, at (402) 977-9140, conference ID 21765940. The webcast will be recorded and available for replay until the company's conference call to discuss financial results for its fourth quarter and fiscal year 2016.
